<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="2.[869,1494,1882,2035]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[869,993,1882,1907]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
Brownish black body, with anterior margin of frons and face yellow; arista black, thickened by dense black short setulae both above and below, with some slightly longer, outstanding hairs on upper side basally; wing membrane yellowish hyaline, with blackish base.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="7" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="2.[869,1493,2074,2131]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[869,1014,2074,2099]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Description:</emphasis>
